       <p>

  <dt>  CD-R/RW
  <dd> <form action="/Agency/install_agent" method="POST">
       name:<input name="agent" value="CDRW"><br>
       type:<input name="type" value="CDRW"><br>
       Samba Names: (for mounting under windows)  archive publish backup
       shared<br>
       SambaConfigFile: <input name="sambaConfig" value="/etc/smb.conf">
<br>
       <input type="submit" value="Install"><br>
       </form>
<dt>  CD-R/RW DOFS form (provides web access to user files on CD-R/RW):
  <dd> <form action="/Agency/install_agent" method="POST">
       name:<input name="agent" value="archive">
       type:<input name="type" value="DOFS"><br>
       root:(absolute) <input name="root" value="&usrDIR;/CDRW/archive">
       <input type="submit" value="Install">
       </form>
<dt>  CD-R/RW DOFS form (provides web access to user files on CD-R/RW):
  <dd> <form action="/Agency/install_agent" method="POST">
       name:<input name="agent" value="publish">
       type:<input name="type" value="DOFS"><br>
